dc_title_s: Hydro (Polygon and Line) Fond du Lac County, WI 2019
dc_description_s: This data group represents hydrography for Fond du Lac County, Wisconsin in 2019 and includes the layers 'DNR_24k_Flowline' and 'DNR_24k_Waterbody'.[DNR_24k_Flowline: Linear Features representing streams and artificial flow through water that are used to form a transport network.DNR_24k_Waterbody: Water features such as Lakes, Reservoirs, Wide Streams and River, and Unspecified Open Water features.]
uw_supplemental_s: Augmented original metadata with UW-Madison specific elements.For access to the most current data for this county, please visit: http://www.fdlco.wi.gov/departments/departments-f-m/land-information/data-download
